<section class="in-app" id="inapp">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow fade-up">In the App</div>
    <h2 class="fade-up delay-1">Feels native.<br><em>Because it is.</em></h2>
    <p class="section-lead fade-up delay-2">AfriGlyph occupies one defined zone in your existing success screen. Nothing else changes. The Glyph plays automatically — no user action required to experience the cultural moment.</p>

    <div class="phone-wrap fade-up delay-2">
      <div class="phone">
        <div class="phone-notch" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="phone-screen">
          <div class="phone-tick" aria-hidden="true">✓</div>
          <div class="phone-title">Transfer successful</div>
          <div class="phone-amount">₦ 50,000</div>
          <div class="phone-sub">To Mum · First Bank</div>
          <div class="glyph-zone">
            <img
              src="/images/glyphs/glyph-hero.jpg"
              alt="Cultural celebration Glyph"
              class="glyph-img"
              width="120"
              height="120"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="tray-peek" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="tray-thumb">
              <img src="/images/glyphs/glyph-tray-1.jpg" alt="" class="glyph-img" width="28" height="28" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="tray-thumb">
              <img src="/images/glyphs/glyph-tray-2.jpg" alt="" class="glyph-img" width="28" height="28" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="tray-thumb">
              <img src="/images/glyphs/glyph-tray-3.jpg" alt="" class="glyph-img" width="28" height="28" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="tray-more">more ›</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="phone-tooltip" aria-hidden="true">Tap to explore more reactions ↑</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="app-features fade-up delay-3">
      <div class="app-feature">
        <div class="app-feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">▶</div>
        <div class="app-feature-title">Auto-play</div>
        <p>The Glyph plays automatically. No tap required for the cultural moment to land.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="app-feature">
        <div class="app-feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">◉</div>
        <div class="app-feature-title">Five curated Glyphs</div>
        <p>Per session, contextually selected. Varied across sessions from a library of 25.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="app-feature">
        <div class="app-feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">↑</div>
        <div class="app-feature-title">Discoverable</div>
        <p>First-session tooltip. Persistent tray peek. No tutorial required after session one.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="app-feature">
        <div class="app-feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">↗</div>
        <div class="app-feature-title">Shareable to WhatsApp</div>
        <p>From the first pilot, every Glyph ships as an animated WhatsApp sticker. Users send them into the conversations that matter — carrying your brand into the channel where African talk actually happens.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
